        "generateUrl": "https://secure.soundcloud.com/authorize",
        "setup": "First create app credentials via [Get an API key](https://developers.soundcloud.com/docs/api/register-app). For user-delegated access, send the user to `https://secure.soundcloud.com/authorize` with your `client_id`, registered `redirect_uri`, `response_type=code`, PKCE `code_challenge`, `code_challenge_method=S256`, and `state`, then exchange the returned code at `https://secure.soundcloud.com/oauth/token` as documented in the [API Guide](https://developers.soundcloud.com/docs/api/guide#authentication). For app-only public-resource access, exchange your app credentials for a token with the client credentials flow at the same token endpoint. Use the returned `access_token` in API calls; refresh with the documented refresh token flow when applicable.",
